	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok the first 2 posts were useless, and the other one was ok but simplistic.<br><br>Ok easiest way to get to ill omen is (now mind you this is info for good races if you happen to be a dark elf wiz I'll get to that in a sec).<br><br>First off go to the docks in Butcher block mt.s (the ones with the little shuttles) then just sit tight on those and it will take you to a larger ship, hop on that and stay on that side or else you might miss the docks when you get to fironia vie (thats the city for good races/classes).<br><br>Once you get there hop off boat and stroll down the docks, then feel free to explore this new city so you get familiar with it.<br><br>Once you find the "bridge" and you eventually will, follow the coast left and go there til you hit the stream (NOTE:: INVIS once you have left the bridge to the land) then follow the stream til you zone into ill omen.<br><br>Once there your just gona have to learn the zone for yourself, try to get a group and have fun at the fort!<br><br>Ok now for the dark elf wizzys, this trip is a bit more dangerous.<br><br>Go to the docks in oasis and wait for the little boat there, once you zone into the timourus deep and the boat comes to a stop get off and follow the right ledge and you'll see some ogres with a dock, once there wait for another larger boat to dock.<br><br>Once on the boat, get off and you arive in the "Overthere" and the small outpost you arrive in is called...well The outpost.This is the city for evil races (not iksars!) it has banks vendors and stuff like other cities.<br><br>WHEW this is alotta typing, from here on you might just wana get someone to show ya the rest of the way, always people heading that way.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
