	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>You're probably hunting in the wrong places.  If a lot of the critters are green or close to it, you won't gain xp very fast.  Of course, if you expect to level at 17 as fast as you levelled at 1-5, forget it.  Levels keep on slowing down throughout the game.  At 17, I recommend highpass orcs.  It's ffa killing there because there's fast spawn that can support more than one group, there's not a set of distinct spots to pull to, and everyone wants to hit everyone else's kills for the faction anyway.  So the group with the wiz is likely to get the kill.  That means a wiz will be very welcome.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
