	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok, hears how you level after level 14:<br>Level 14-16: Lavastorm.  This is great experience.  Just pull to the Najena Zone and if you get in trouble zone.<br>Level 16-20: Highpass Hold.  Try and get into an orc group.<br>Level 20-23: Lake Rathe.  Great experience if you get up early and get a aviak spawn.<br>Level 24-28: South Karana.  Get in Aviak groups and kill aviaks at the treehouse.  You can also (if not worried about Qeynos faction) kill treants.<br>Level 28: Splitpaw Gnolls<br>Level 29-33: Kite Splitpaw gnolls and aviak avocets.<br>Level 33-40: The overthere:  Kite monsters at the ledge.<br>This is as far as I have gotten.<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Aline Griffonfeather of Povar<br>Erudite Channeler of the 52nd Season</td></tr>
